logic_summary: Supplemented V2 with 'Aided Piano Verification' test to explicitly capture the subjective functional verification process described in the text.

value.name: Aided Piano Verification
value.result_summary: Gain reduction of 15 dB at 274 Hz and 554 Hz yielded no subjective improvement. Notch filtering of 15 dB in the 1000–1500 Hz region substantially improved the sound quality of the piano.
